      "content": "it's just so exhausting. every day is just acting. pretending to be someone who belongs in a lab or a lecture hall or even just a dinner party. it feels like being a ghost haunted by my own mistakes. people see the scientist, but i'm just the emptiness behind the mask. i'm tired of the performance. i'm just so tired of pretending that there's a \"real\" me to save.",
